edu.um.cps2002.tile_game

Class Team

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.um.cps2002.tile_game.Subject
      • edu.um.cps2002.tile_game.Team

  • public class Team
extends Subject
    The Team class is an subclass of the Subject class and represents teams of players. It is used to implement the observer design pattern, acting as the concrete subject.
    Author:
    Luke Collins & Stefania Damato
